    "• Bypassing LLM Defenses.",
    "Leveraging the new understanding of LLM chatbot defenses, we successfully bypass these mechanisms using strategic manipulations of time-sensitive responses, highlighting previously ignored vulnerabilities in the mainstream LLM chatbots.",
